OL,3,CJunior doctors in NI set to strike
OL,5,FJunior doctors in Northern Ireland
OL,6,Fhave voted in favour of taking strike
OL,7,Faction.
OL,9,FThe doctors are to walk out of work
OL,10,Ffor 24 hours from 8am on March 6.
OL,12,FThey are calling for better pay inline
OL,13,Fwith their counterparts in the rest of
OL,14,Fthe UK.
OL,16,FJunior doctors working in Northern
OL,17,FIreland range from being newly
OL,18,Fqualified doctors earning less than
OL,19,F#13 per-hour basic pay to experienced
OL,20,Fsurgeons earning #30 per-hour basic
OL,21,Fpay.
