OL,3,CJunior doctors in NI set to strike
OL,5,FThe BMA said there was a 68.7% turnout
OL,6,Ffor the ballot with 97.6% of those
OL,7,Fvoting yes to a full 24-hour walkout.
OL,9,FIt follows similar industrial action
OL,10,Fin other parts of the UK.
OL,12,FDr Fiona Griffin, chair of BMA's
OL,13,FNorthern Ireland junior doctors
OL,14,Fcommittee, said the yes vote is "a
OL,15,Fclear indication of the strength of
OL,16,Ffeeling among junior doctors about
OL,17,Fyears of pay erosion".
