OL,3,CJunior doctors in NI set to strike
OL,5,F"It is clear from this result that
OL,6,Fjunior doctors feel they have no other
OL,7,Foption but to strike. We owe it to
OL,8,Fourselves, our patients and the future
OL,9,Fof the health service to act," said Dr
OL,10,FGriffin.
