OL,3,CJunior doctors in NI set to strike
OL,5,F"We have had 16 years of pay erosion
OL,6,Fwhich now amounts to over 30% loss of
OL,7,Fpay, yet in this time our workload and
OL,8,Fburnout levels have risen. Coupled
OL,9,Fwith rising inflation this is a huge
OL,10,Ffinancial loss for anyone in any
OL,11,Fprofession, but it is causing an acute
OL,12,Fworkforce crisis among junior doctors
OL,13,Fas many are thinking about leaving
OL,14,FNorthern Ireland to work elsewhere for
OL,15,Fbetter pay and working conditions,
OL,16,Fwhere the complex and skilled work we
OL,17,Fundertake is properly rewarded.
