OL,3,CJunior doctors in NI set to strike
OL,5,F"These are the consultants, GPs and
OL,6,Fspecialty doctors of the future,
OL,7,Fmedics that we are relying on to drive
OL,8,Fdown our waiting lists."
OL,10,FDr Griffin said a recent pay meeting
OL,11,Fbetween Department of Health officials
OL,12,Fleft them feeling "extremely
OL,13,Fdisappointed and disheartened".
