OL,3,CJunior doctors in NI set to strike
OL,5,F"We entered that meeting with the hope
OL,6,Fthat good faith negotiations would
OL,7,Fcommence on doctor's pay asks. Instead
OL,8,Fwe were presented with a fait accompli
OL,9,Fof a below inflation 6% uplift, that
OL,10,Fwill be awarded in the next financial
OL,11,Fyear. We were told any further
OL,12,Fdiscussions on pay had to be delayed
OL,13,Funtil the ongoing Westminster pay
OL,14,Fnegotiations with doctors in England
OL,15,Fhad concluded, despite health and pay
OL,16,Fbeing devolved matters.
