OL,3,CJunior doctors in NI set to strike
OL,5,F"All of this is simply unacceptable
OL,6,Fand is far from the spirit of
OL,7,Fmeaningful engagement on pay. It
OL,8,Ffurther adds to the sense that the
OL,9,Frole doctors play in the health
OL,10,Fservice is simply not valued."
OL,12,FDr Griffin called on the Health
OL,13,FMinister and the Executive to fight
OL,14,Ffor proper investment in the health
OL,15,Fservice's key asset ` its staff.
