OL,3,CJunior doctors in NI set to strike
OL,5,F"Junior doctors must be paid fairly
OL,6,Ffor the work that we do and that means
OL,7,Fnothing less than an immediate, above
OL,8,Finflation pay award and a commitment
OL,9,Fto full pay restoration to 2008
OL,10,Flevels," she said.J"The future of our
OL,11,Fprofession and our health service
OL,12,Fdepends on this issue being addressed
OL,13,Furgently and we are willing to get
OL,14,Faround the negotiating table at any
OL,15,Ftime to achieve this. I also call on
OL,16,Fall political representatives to show
OL,17,Ftheir support and join us on the
OL,18,Fpicket lines on 6 March."
OL,20,FUTV has asked the Health Department
OL,21,Ffor a statement.
